# _redirects — Cloudflare Pages
#
# Format: /source-path   destination   status-code
# External redirects (to a different domain) are fully supported.
#
# ── Legacy internal apply system → external application form ─────────────────
# The internal /apply/ pages are no longer in use. All applications are handled
# by the external form at https://apply-choice-properties.pages.dev.
# These rules catch any old email links or bookmarks and send them to the right place.
#
/apply.html                 https://apply-choice-properties.pages.dev                      301
/apply/login.html           https://apply-choice-properties.pages.dev/?path=dashboard      301
/apply/dashboard.html       https://apply-choice-properties.pages.dev/?path=dashboard      301
/apply/success.html         https://apply-choice-properties.pages.dev/?path=dashboard      301
/apply/lease.html           https://apply-choice-properties.pages.dev                      301
/apply/*                    https://apply-choice-properties.pages.dev/?path=dashboard      301
